# Stellar Frontend Design System

## 1. Typography

### Font Families

| Font | Tailwind Class | Source | Usage |
|------|---------------|--------|-------|
| **GT America Trial** | `font-sans` (default) | Local `@font-face` in `typography.css` | Default body, UI elements |
| **PP Agrandir** | `font-agrandir` | Local `@font-face` in `typography.css` (`"PP Agrandir"`) | Brand headings |
| **Inter** | `font-inter` | Google Fonts CDN (`index.html`) | Specific UI elements |
| **Poppins** | `font-poppins` | Google Fonts CDN (`index.html`) | Auth pages only |

### Font Size Scale (h1300 → h100)

```
h1300: 32px  — PP Agrandir, -1px ls     h700: 16px — GT America Bold
h1250: 28px  — PP Agrandir              h600: 16px — GT America Medium
h1100: 24px  — PP Agrandir, -1px ls     h550: 16px — GT America Regular
h1050: 24px  — GT America Medium        h500: 14px — GT America Bold
h1000: 20px  — GT America Medium        h450: 14px — GT America/Inter Medium
h900:  18px  — GT America Medium        h400: 14px — GT America Regular
h800:  18px  — GT America, -0.2px ls    h300: 12px — GT America Medium
h750:  18px  — GT America Regular       h200: 12px — GT America Regular
                                        h100: 10px — GT America Medium
```

```tsx
<h1 className="text-h1300 font-agrandir">Title</h1>
<p className="text-h400">Body text</p>
```

