## 2. Color System

### Sandstorm (Backgrounds & Borders)
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `s0` | #F9F9F6 | Primary background |
| `s5` | #FEFEFB | Text field bg |
| `s10` | #FCFCF9 | Background 1 |
| `s20` | #F5F4EF | Background 2 |
| `s30` | #F0F0ED | Hover |
| `s40` | #E8E8E3 | Border / Press |
| `s50` | #E4E4D7 | Border 1 |
| `s60` | #D1D1C7 | Border 2 |
| `s70` | #73726C | Dark border |

### Forest Green (Primary Brand)
| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `f0` | #DCF1E8 | Lightest |
| `f10` | #D6E5E5 | Disabled text |
| `f20` | #9BB1B0 | Light accent |
| `f30` | #506766 | Secondary text |
| `f40` | #136D6D | **Primary action** |
| `f50` | #0E4E4E | Primary hover |
| `f60` | #072929 | Primary text |

### Other Palettes (key values)
- **Blue**: b10 `#3370FF`, b100 `#74AAFD` (links), b400 `#0350C3`
- **Red**: r0 `#FFEBE6` (error bg), r30 `#CE1313` (error), r40 `#B51111`
- **Yellow**: y10 `#FF991F` (warning), y50 `#FFFAE6`
- **Purple**: p500 `#403294` (status)
- **Neutral**: n0 (#FFF) → n1000 (#000205), plus alpha variants (n10A–n900A)

### Semantic Tokens
```tsx
text-text-primary / text-text-secondary / text-text-disabled / text-text-inverse
bg-background-primary / bg-background-secondary / bg-background-field
border-border-default / border-border-light / border-border-medium
text-status-primary / text-status-danger / text-status-warning
```

### CSS Custom Properties
Colors also available as `var(--color-forest-f40)`, `var(--color-semantic-text-primary)`, etc. in `@theme` block of `index.css`. Use for CSS classes only — prefer Tailwind utilities in components.

