## 6. Styling

### Dual System
1. **Tailwind utilities** — for component-level styling (preferred for new components)
2. **CSS classes in `index.css`** — for shared patterns (see `css-component-classes.mdc`)

| Situation | Use |
|-----------|-----|
| New component | Tailwind utilities |
| Tables | `.table-*` CSS classes |
| Campaign forms | `.campaign-input`, `.form-label` |
| Data view buttons | `.edit-button`, `.create-entity-button` |
| Tabs | `.tab-button`, `.tabs-container` |
| Loading | `.loading-overlay` |

### Token Studio Pipeline
Colors sourced from Token Studio → `tailwind-colors-generated` → `tailwind.config.ts`. Also duplicated as CSS vars in `@theme` block of `index.css`.

