## 9. Responsive & Accessibility

- **Breakpoints**: sm 640, md 768, lg 1024, xl 1280, 2xl 1536
- **Mobile-first**, min 44px touch targets
- **Semantic HTML**: `<button>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, proper heading hierarchy
- **ARIA labels**: required on icon-only buttons
- **Focus states**: `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forest-f40`
- **Color contrast**: WCAG AA minimum
- **Alt text**: required on all `<img>`

